As long as your list of results isn't too big, skip the pagination and just give the user one big sortable list and a text box for instantly filtering results.

Adapted from:

http://ejohn.org/blog/jquery-livesearch/#postcomment

http://orderedlist.com/blog/articles/live-search-with-quicksilver-style-for-jquery/

